{#
  Monochrome tag glyphs from Lucide (lucide.dev, ISC license), inlined as SVG so
  they inherit currentColor and the light/dark theme. Keyed by the `icon` field
  on each catalog entry's access_tags (see _data/catalog.js). Sized to the
  surrounding text (1em); add a case here when introducing a new tag icon.

  Pass `title` to make the icon self-describing: it becomes the native hover
  tooltip and the accessible label. Omit it for a purely decorative icon that
  sits next to its own visible text label.
#}
{%- macro tagIcon(name, title="") -%}
